text: Novobiktovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Takarlikovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 553 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Novobiktovo
